$ Powershell module WinConfig: add-dirToPath
@ add-dirToPath

`add-dirToPath` adds a director to user's or machine's `→ Windows/development/environment-variables/PATH` or
→ Windows/development/environment-variables#win-envvar-PSModulePath[`PSModulePath`] environment variable.

code {
add-dirToPath $pwd
add-dirToPath $pwd -machine
add-dirToPath $pwd -psModulePath
code }

sa:
  This function is found in the PowerShell module `→ Windows/PowerShell/modules/personal/WinConfig`.
